Detailed Description

Dictionary type base class.

Provides a base class for a dictionary type data structure.

virtual std::string ORVDictValue::GetStringOfValue (  )  const [pure virtual]

Returns a string of the value.

For example, for the number 1, it would return a string "1". This is useful for generating a string output of a dictionary.
